        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued May 18 at 1:00PM CDT until May 18 at 1:15PM CDT by NWS Tulsa OK</headline>
        <description>At 100 PM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 4 miles northeast of
Maysville, moving northeast at 40 mph.

HAZARD...Quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Damage to vehicles is expected.

Locations in or near the path include...
Maysville...                      Gravette...
</description>
